📌JOIN IAS SC

🎨 FOR SALE: Soft Pastels – ₱750 🎨

Selling my used soft pastels! 💛 Some sticks are untouched, while a few have minor quirks (Cool Gray 3 is split into 2, and Ivory + Cool Gray 3/4/5 have torn wrappings) but all still totally usable.
I’m letting them go because I’m no longer into visual arts and pang dagdag baon na rin 😂
💌 DM me if you’re interested!

message.text:
PubCon is my Home!🏠

For almost 3 years, this division has shaped me and given me the space to showcase my talents and skills.

Because of PubCon, I was able to host on various stages in FEU and even outside the university. The opportunities they provided opened doors for me, and many of my professors began to acknowledge my efforts and growth.

One thing I’ll never forget is when my professor told me: “Grabe ka Heart!, hindi ko akalain na ganun ka kagaling.” Those words continue to inspire me until today.

Through my division, I also learned how to create engaging content that connects with students—a skill I’ll carry with me beyond college.

PubCon is more than just PubCon.
It shapes who you are, creates better opportunities, and allows us to interact with different kinds of people.

Kaya ano pa hinihintay niyo??? 

 Sumali na kayo dito sa Publicity and Contents Division!! 💗🤗

SEE YOUU!! 👀

Apply now and be part of FEU IABF SC!
📌IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
📌Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
📌PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

message.text:
PubCon is my Home!🏠

For almost 3 years, this division has shaped me and given me the space to showcase my talents and skills.

Because of PubCon, I was able to host on various stages in FEU and even outside the university. The opportunities they provided opened doors for me, and many of my professors began to acknowledge my efforts and growth.

One thing I’ll never forget is when my professor told me: “Grabe ka Heart!, hindi ko akalain na ganun ka kagaling.” Those words continue to inspire me until today.

Through my division, I also learned how to create engaging content that connects with students—a skill I’ll carry with me beyond college.

PubCon is more than just PubCon.
It shapes who you are, creates better opportunities, and allows us to interact with different kinds of people.

Kaya ano pa hinihintay niyo??? 

 Sumali na kayo dito sa Publicity and Contents Division!! 💗🤗

SEE YOUU!! 👀

📌IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M

message.text:
PubCon is my Home!🏠

For almost 3 years, this division has shaped me and given me the space to showcase my talents and skills.

Because of PubCon, I was able to host on various stages in FEU and even outside the university. The opportunities they provided opened doors for me, and many of my professors began to acknowledge my efforts and growth.

One thing I’ll never forget is when my professor told me: “Grabe ka Heart!, hindi ko akalain na ganun ka kagaling.” Those words continue to inspire me until today.

Through my division, I also learned how to create engaging content that connects with students—a skill I’ll carry with me beyond college.

PubCon is more than just PubCon.
It shapes who you are, creates better opportunities, and allows us to interact with different kinds of people.

Kaya ano pa hinihintay niyo??? 

 Sumali na kayo dito sa Publicity and Contents Division!! 💗🤗

SEE YOUU!! 👀

Apply now and be part of FEU IABF SC!
📌IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
📌Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
📌PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL
